reviewText: good to see tevin come back strong.
OK

THE CONCERT SHOWS THAT TEVIN CAN STILL SING.  IT IS VERY ENJOYABLE CONCERT AND VERY CLEAR.
THE ONLY COMPLAINT IS YOU COULD NOT HEAR THE BACKGROUND SINGERS AT ALL ON THE FIRST CONCERT
AND VERY LITTLE ON THE 2ND CONCERT, WHICH IAM SURE WAS NOT THE CASE AT THE ACTUAL CONCERT.
REGARDLESS IT WAS STILL VERY ENJOYABLE TO WATCH.
He can sing anymore his best song on here is his new one.
2 concerts the last one is the best band sound tighter and Tevin sounds better.

It's okay. Cheesy band though.  They sound awful at times. He still sounds the same though. And for some reason it says promo or something on the screen. Like I said it had the potential to be great, but I watched it once and put it away
Great to see Tevin in concert.  The band was great too.  He is all grown up but I couldn't help seeing him as a youngster.

Tevin amazes me with how shy he comes across in some of these performances. I can sense his humbleness through the screen. I admire that; for someone with sooooo much talent to be so down to earth. I love his interaction with the crowd and his smile is so infectious.
The world is dying to see more of you, Tevin! Thanks for the DVD. Pure perfection!

Natasha Dodson
I really loved Tevin Campbell DVD !! He  sounds great! He needs a record deal for new music for sure! We are missing this voice and his sound! Way to go Tevin!! Come to Atlanra I would go see you!!

It's so amazing tevin is a true talent I truly love him his music touches my soul tevin has a special place in my heart and he is truly a blessing to be comin back to music he's an amazing singer I'm a huge TevinCampbell fan and I will always love him 100% thumbs up I give this DVD an A
